# DATABASE TABLES DETAILED DOCUMENTATION

## Database Overview
- **Database System:** PostgreSQL 15+
- **Total Tables:** 37 tables across 11 business domains
- **ORM:** SQLAlchemy 2.0+ (Async)
- **Migration Tool:** Alembic

## DOMAIN 1: IAM (Identity & Access Management) - 4 Tables

### **Table: iam_users**
```sql
CREATE TABLE iam_users (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    email VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    username VARCHAR(100) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    password_hash VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    role VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT 'user' CHECK (role IN ('admin', 'user', 'viewer')),
    is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
    is_verified BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    email_verified BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    phone_verified BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    two_factor_enabled BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    last_login TIMESTAMP,
    failed_login_attempts INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
    locked_until TIMESTAMP,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    deleted_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Indexes
CREATE INDEX idx_iam_users_email ON iam_users(email);
CREATE INDEX idx_iam_users_username ON iam_users(username);
CREATE INDEX idx_iam_users_role ON iam_users(role);
CREATE INDEX idx_iam_users_active ON iam_users(is_active);
CREATE INDEX idx_iam_users_created_at ON iam_users(created_at);

-- Business Rules:
-- - Email must be unique and valid format
-- - Username must be 3-30 characters, alphanumeric and underscore only
-- - Password must be hashed with bcrypt (min 12 salt rounds)
-- - Account locked after 5 failed login attempts for 30 minutes
-- - Soft delete with deleted_at timestamp
-- - Role-based access control (admin, user, viewer)
```

### **Table: iam_user_profiles**
```sql
CREATE TABLE iam_user_profiles (
    user_id INTEGER REFERENCES iam_users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    first_name VARCHAR(100),
    last_name VARCHAR(100),
    display_name VARCHAR(200),
    avatar_url TEXT,
    bio TEXT CHECK (LENGTH(bio) <= 1000),
    company VARCHAR(200),
    job_title VARCHAR(150),
    website_url TEXT,
    location VARCHAR(200),
    timezone VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT 'UTC',
    language VARCHAR(10) DEFAULT 'en',
    country VARCHAR(2),
    phone VARCHAR(20),
    birth_date DATE,
    gender VARCHAR(20),
    social_links JSONB DEFAULT '{}',
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id)
);

-- Business Rules:
-- - One profile per user (1:1 relationship)
-- - Avatar images must be validated for size and type
-- - Bio limited to 1000 characters
-- - Social links stored as JSONB for flexibility
-- - Timezone must be valid IANA timezone
-- - Country code must be ISO 3166-1 alpha-2
```

### **Table: iam_user_preferences**
```sql
CREATE TABLE iam_user_preferences (
    user_id INTEGER REFERENCES iam_users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    theme VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'light' CHECK (theme IN ('light', 'dark', 'auto')),
    sidebar_collapsed BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    default_model VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT 'gpt-4',
    notifications_enabled BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
    email_notifications BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
    push_notifications BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    auto_save BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
    auto_save_interval INTEGER DEFAULT 30 CHECK (auto_save_interval BETWEEN 10 AND 300),
    display_density VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'comfortable' CHECK (display_density IN ('compact', 'comfortable', 'spacious')),
    date_format VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'YYYY-MM-DD',
    time_format VARCHAR(10) DEFAULT '24h' CHECK (time_format IN ('12h', '24h')),
    currency VARCHAR(3) DEFAULT 'USD',
    number_format VARCHAR(10) DEFAULT 'en-US',
    dashboard_layout JSONB DEFAULT '{}',
    quick_actions JSONB DEFAULT '[]',
    keyboard_shortcuts JSONB DEFAULT '{}',
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    PRIMARY KEY (user_id)
);

-- Business Rules:
-- - One preference set per user (1:1 relationship)
-- - Auto-save interval between 10-300 seconds
-- - Dashboard layout stored as JSONB for flexibility
-- - Quick actions array for customizable shortcuts
-- - Keyboard shortcuts customization support
```

### **Table: iam_user_sessions**
```sql
CREATE TABLE iam_user_sessions (
    id UUID PRIMARY KEY DEFAULT gen_random_uuid(),
    user_id INTEGER REFERENCES iam_users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    session_token VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE NOT NULL,
    refresh_token VARCHAR(255) UNIQUE,
    device_info JSONB,
    ip_address INET,
    user_agent TEXT,
    browser_name VARCHAR(100),
    browser_version VARCHAR(50),
    os_name VARCHAR(100),
    os_version VARCHAR(50),
    device_type VARCHAR(50),
    is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
    is_mobile BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    last_activity TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    expires_at TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP
);

-- Business Rules:
-- - Maximum 5 active sessions per user
-- - Session expires after 24 hours of inactivity
-- - Automatic cleanup of expired sessions (daily job)
-- - Device fingerprinting for security
-- - IP address tracking for suspicious activity detection
```

## DOMAIN 2: AI_AGENTS (Agent Management) - 3 Tables

### **Table: ai_agents**
```sql
CREATE TABLE ai_agents (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(200) NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    user_id INTEGER REFERENCES iam_users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    agent_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL CHECK (agent_type IN ('conversational', 'task_specific', 'analytical', 'creative')),
    model_provider VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL CHECK (model_provider IN ('openai', 'anthropic', 'google', 'cohere', 'local')),
    model_name VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    model_version VARCHAR(50),
    system_prompt TEXT CHECK (LENGTH(system_prompt) <= 10000),
    temperature DECIMAL(3,2) DEFAULT 0.7 CHECK (temperature >= 0 AND temperature <= 2),
    max_tokens INTEGER DEFAULT 2048 CHECK (max_tokens > 0 AND max_tokens <= 32000),
    top_p DECIMAL(3,2) DEFAULT 1.0 CHECK (top_p >= 0 AND top_p <= 1),
    frequency_penalty DECIMAL(3,2) DEFAULT 0.0 CHECK (frequency_penalty >= -2 AND frequency_penalty <= 2),
    presence_penalty DECIMAL(3,2) DEFAULT 0.0 CHECK (presence_penalty >= -2 AND presence_penalty <= 2),
    stop_sequences TEXT[],
    custom_parameters JSONB DEFAULT '{}',
    is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
    is_public BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    is_featured BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    usage_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
    rating_average DECIMAL(3,2) DEFAULT 0.0,
    rating_count INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
    tags TEXT[],
    category VARCHAR(100),
    subcategory VARCHAR(100),
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    deleted_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Business Rules:
-- - Agent name must be unique per user
-- - System prompt limited to 10,000 characters
-- - Model parameters must be within valid ranges
-- - Public agents can be used by other users
-- - Featured agents promoted in marketplace
-- - Usage tracking for analytics
-- - Rating system for quality assessment
-- - Soft delete with deleted_at timestamp
```

## DOMAIN 3: COMMUNICATION (Chat System) - 3 Tables

### **Table: communication_conversations**
```sql
CREATE TABLE communication_conversations (
    id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INTEGER REFERENCES iam_users(id) ON DELETE CASCADE,
    agent_id INTEGER REFERENCES ai_agents(id) ON DELETE SET NULL,
    title VARCHAR(300),
    conversation_type VARCHAR(50) DEFAULT 'chat' CHECK (conversation_type IN ('chat', 'support', 'training', 'analysis')),
    status VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'active' CHECK (status IN ('active', 'paused', 'completed', 'archived')),
    priority VARCHAR(20) DEFAULT 'normal' CHECK (priority IN ('low', 'normal', 'high', 'urgent')),
    language VARCHAR(10) DEFAULT 'en',
    is_active BOOLEAN DEFAULT true,
    is_archived BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    is_pinned BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    is_shared BOOLEAN DEFAULT false,
    share_token UUID,
    context_data JSONB DEFAULT '{}',
    metadata JSONB DEFAULT '{}',
    summary TEXT,
    sentiment_score DECIMAL(3,2),
    satisfaction_rating INTEGER CHECK (satisfaction_rating BETWEEN 1 AND 5),
    total_messages INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
    total_tokens INTEGER DEFAULT 0,
    total_cost DECIMAL(10,4) DEFAULT 0,
    started_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    ended_at TIMESTAMP,
    last_message_at TIMESTAMP,
    created_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    updated_at TIMESTAMP DEFAULT CURRENT_TIMESTAMP,
    archived_at TIMESTAMP
);

-- Business Rules:
-- - Auto-generated title from first message
-- - Conversation types for categorization
-- - Status workflow management
-- - Sharing capability with secure tokens
-- - Context preservation across sessions
-- - Sentiment analysis integration
-- - Automatic archiving after 90 days inactivity
-- - Token and cost tracking
```

